# Cloudinary Configuration
# Get these from your Cloudinary dashboard: https://cloudinary.com/console
VITE_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name_here
VITE_CLOUDINARY_UPLOAD_PRESET=your_unsigned_upload_preset_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual Cloudinary credentials
# 3. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 4. For Vercel deployment, set these in the Environment Variables settings